      <title>乌克兰要求苹果、谷歌合作打击军事赌博</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/war-in-ukraine-zelenskiy-enlists-apple-google-in-military-gambling-crackdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基已禁止该国军队内赌博，因为担心赌博会削弱士气并在对抗俄罗斯入侵的过程中构成安全风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/war-in-ukraine-zelenskiy-enlists-apple-google-in-military-gambling-crackdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 10:20:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯计划在炼油厂遭受最近袭击后采取反无人机应对措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/russia-plans-anti-drone-response-after-recent-hits-on-refineries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在无人机多次袭击乌克兰邻近地区以及对距离边境较远的目标（特别是炼油厂）进行袭击后，俄罗斯正在加强对抗无人机的军事训练。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/russia-plans-anti-drone-response-after-recent-hits-on-refineries</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 08:41:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>西班牙试图取缔分离主义者：现在由他们做主</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/basque-elections-may-see-upset-by-eta-linked-party-bildu</link>
      <description><![CDATA[西班牙政府释放了因与巴斯克恐怖组织“埃塔”有联系而入狱的活动人士后，大多数人就消失在了幕后。但阿纳尔多·奥特吉则不然。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/basque-elections-may-see-upset-by-eta-linked-party-bildu</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克进入卢旺达移民计划最后阶段，保守党担心新的失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/rishi-sunak-enters-rwanda-migration-plan-endgame-with-uk-tories-fearing-failure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)的旗舰移民政策下周进入尾声，一些保守党人士担心这位总理让自己暴露在他所押注的首相职位问题上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/rishi-sunak-enters-rwanda-migration-plan-endgame-with-uk-tories-fearing-failure</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据英国《金融时报》报道，苏纳克预计将宣布新的英国军舰计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/sunak-expected-to-announce-new-uk-warship-program-ft-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国《金融时报》援引不愿透露姓名的知情人士的话报道称，英国首相苏纳克正准备宣布一项新的军舰计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/sunak-expected-to-announce-new-uk-warship-program-ft-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 04:12:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉反对派在令人惊讶的转折中团结在候选人周围</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/venezuela-election-opposition-picks-edmundo-gonzalez-to-challenge-maduro</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉反对派围绕即将举行的投票的暂定候选人团结起来，这种团结的表现可能对总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗的连任构成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/venezuela-election-opposition-picks-edmundo-gonzalez-to-challenge-maduro</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 03:10:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南加州大学在告别演说争议中取消毕业典礼演讲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/usc-cancels-commencement-speakers-amid-valedictorian-controversy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南加州大学在即将举行的毕业典礼上取消了所有外部演讲者，此前因取消 2024 届毕业生致辞演讲的决定而遭到强烈反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/usc-cancels-commencement-speakers-amid-valedictorian-controversy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 02:10:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普审判外自焚男子因伤重死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-19/police-to-review-security-outside-courthouse-hosting-trump-s-trial-after-man-sets-himself-on-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约（美联社）——警方称，一名男子在前总统唐纳德·特朗普受审的法院外浇上助燃剂并自焚，现已死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-04-19/police-to-review-security-outside-courthouse-hosting-trump-s-trial-after-man-sets-himself-on-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 20:29:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>在纽约市特朗普审判外自焚的男子已经死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/man-who-self-immolated-outside-nyc-trump-trial-in-critical-state</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据美联社援引警方消息称，一名佛罗里达州男子在曼哈顿市中心法院大楼外自焚，唐纳德·特朗普的刑事审判正在进行中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/man-who-self-immolated-outside-nyc-trump-trial-in-critical-state</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 19:11:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乍得要求美国停止战略陆军基地的行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/chad-asks-us-troops-to-cease-operations-at-strategic-army-base</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乍得呼吁美国从中非国家的一个军事基地撤军，该基地是西方为数不多的打击该地区激烈圣战叛乱的前哨基地之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/chad-asks-us-troops-to-cease-operations-at-strategic-army-base</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 15:16:49 GMT</pubDate>
